latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Bringing Cajun Flavours to India, Jubilant Foodworks Limited (JFL), India’s leading food services player, has launched the iconic US Fried Chicken brand Popeyes® in India, with the grand opening of its first restaurant in Bengaluru today. 

Popeyes®, best known for its spicy New Orleans style fried chicken & Chicken Sandwich, aims to delight Indian guests with the bold and delicious flavours of its Louisiana-style chicken.
 

Louisiana born, Popeyes® was founded in 1972 and has been one of America’s most popular and fastest growing Chicken brands.
 
The success of Popeyes® lies in its traditional and unique technique of hand breading, battering, and marinating its fresh chicken for 12 hours in bold Cajun seasonings. The Cajun seasoning has a blend of cayenne pepper, garlic, onion, black pepper, celery and white pepper and offers an unbeatably bold and flavourful culinary experience.
.
.
.
Video courtesy @popeyes_india 
#neveradullmoment #clientdiaries #buzzybee #bangalore #food #cajunchicken #foodie #justlaunched

Raw Mango & Anjali Singh create new conversations in wildlife conservation through textile and design - SHER BAGH!
This limited-edition collection highlights humanity’s relationship with nature and wildlife while raising awareness for India’s critically endangered animal life.
A collaboration that was in the making for over 3 years, SHER BAGH arrives in Raw Mango Mumbai, Raw Mango Lodhi New Delhi & Raw Mango Online from 12th December. It will also be available at SUJÁN Jawai, & SUJÁN Sher Bagh, boutiques towards the end of the year.
5% of all sales of the Anjali Singh x Raw Mango ‘SHER BAGH’ collection will be directly donated to SUJÁN’s conservation projects in the region of Jawai (visit: thesujanlife.com/conservation) thus directly contributing to restoring, preserving and expanding precious wilderness habitats.
.
.
.
#rawmango #wildlife #limitededition #thesujanlife #sujan #coexistence #fallwinter2021 #indianweaves #clientdiaries #neveradullmoment #brandstorytelling #prpundit

latestIgtvVideos.title: There is no Planet B
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
From the very beginning, Panerai’s destiny has been inseparable from the marine environment. With its history of inventing state-of-the-art instruments for the Italian Navy and daring modern-day heroes, the brand’s watchmaking heritage is derived from its profound respect for the ocean. 
Panerai is partnering with the Intergovernmental Oceanographic Commission of UNESCO Development, the agency responsible for implementing the Ocean Decade. 

The aim is to invest, speak out and establish a path forward, embracing more responsible thinking and behaviour toward the ocean and its preservation, by developing educational and research initiatives, providing information and fostering an active community. 

From 2021 to 2030, the Ocean Decade will promote science-based management of the ocean and marine resources to achieve the goals of the 2030 Agenda for Sustainable Development. 

.
.
.

latestPosts.caption:
Get ready for Season 3 of ‘ALCHEMY’— A Premier Case Study Challenge by #PRPunditHavasRed for Emerging Communicators changemakers!

Initiative supported by Comms News and Reputation Today, Alchemy 2025 is more than just a competition- it’s a transformative journey for emerging communicators to showcase creativity, critical thinking, and strategic prowess.

Guided by industry mentors and assessed by a stellar jury of marketing and comms leaders, participants will gain invaluable experience and insights. Top teams will win passes to PRAXIS 2025, and the winning team will receive an all-expense-paid trip to a premier international communications conference!

🔓 Free entry 
🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Participate as a duo 
📍 Open to PR professionals (agency/corporate communications experts) aged 30 or below, residing in India

📅 Last date to send nominations: 15 June 2025
📧 Email your entries to: alchemy@prpundithavasred.com

For more details, visit: bit.ly/RTALCHEMY3

Let’s ignite ideas. Inspire impact. Create PR magic.

#Alchemy2025 #PRChallenge #NextGenPR #StrategicCommunication #PRCaseStudy
